      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior cabin, every detail confirms its status as a collector-grade acquisition. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands absolute perfection.",
