      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain is mechanically flawless. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent overhaul of the high-pressure VANOS system and rod bearings\u2014essential preventative maintenance for this high-performance mill. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains a deep, swirl-free luster with all factory VIN tags intact. Handling is sharpened by the factory M-Variable differential lock and refreshed suspension geometry, ensuring the communicative steering feel these cars are famed for. This is a turn-key, concours-ready specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
